##This first model is intended to help me understand machine learning principles without using ML libraries**
**This model is a rudimentary neural network model that will NOT take into account the complexities of drafting such as positional needs of individual teams or success of college teams**
**For this first model, I will only be using the statistics of individual players to predict the likelihood of them being drafted**
**Since roughly 25% of the NFL roster is made up of SEC players, this model will be built to predict only the likelihood of SEC players being drafted**
**This model will only include data from the last ten years: 2015-2025.**
**Only the top 200 ranked defensive players in the SEC will be included in the training dataset.**



